title: Rannvijay Singh’s Super Sweet Birthday Wish For His Wife Prianca
text:
Swagata Dam Mar . 7 . 2017 
Rannvijay Singh dotes on his wife and he never ceases to give us #HusbandGoals. He’s well-ready, witty, SO HANDSOME, super caring and most importantly, he respects women. And all that makes him the perfect man to be with. After being a great hubby to Prianca , he’s now playing the role of a loving daddy to his baby girl Kainat . On the occassion of his beloved wife’s birthday, Rannvijay posted this cute wish on Instagram. A post shared by Rannvijay (@rannvijaysingha) on Mar 7, 2017 at 12:32am PST 
Aww!
